<section xmlns="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook" xml:id="DisableWbem" version="5.0">
 <title xml:id="SysMgmtServices">Disable WBEM</title>
 <para>
  Disables the Solaris Web-Based Enterprise Management (WBEM) services.
  <indexterm>
   <primary>WBEM</primary>
  </indexterm>
 </para>
 <para>
  If there is no need to use web-based management applications or the
  Sun Management Console (SMC), it is recommended to apply this module.
 </para>
